(7, '2021-07-28 18:16:59.757909', '2021-07-28 18:23:33.387232', '\'simplemde-markdown-editor\' avec mathjax  ou Katex', '**Avec mathjax **\r\nDÉMO : <https://jsfiddle.net/1wkojtaa/3/>\r\n\r\n<https://gist.github.com/chooco13/c280c1cc6584c97af85307028ecaebb1>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n`<html>\r\n<head>\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/simplemde/latest/simplemde.min.css\">\r\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/simplemde/latest/simplemde.min.js\"></script>\r\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mathjax/2.7.2/MathJax.js?config=TeX-MML-AM_CHTML\"></script>\r\n    <script src=\"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.min.js\" integrity=\"sha256-hwg4gsxgFZhOsEEamdOYGBf13FyQuiTwlAQgxVSNgt4=\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>\r\n\r\n    <script>\r\n        $(function () {\r\n            MathJax.Hub.Config({\r\n                tex2jax: {inlineMath: [[\"$\",\"$\"],[\"\\\\(\",\"\\\\)\"]]}\r\n            });\r\n            \r\n            var QUEUE = MathJax.Hub.queue;\r\n            var simplemde = new SimpleMDE({\r\n                element: document.getElementById(\"md-editor\"),\r\n                spellChecker: false,\r\n                previewRender: function(plainText) {\r\n                    var preview = document.getElementsByClassName(\"editor-preview-side\")[0];\r\n                    preview.innerHTML = this.parent.markdown(plainText);\r\n                    preview.setAttribute(\'id\',\'editor-preview\')\r\n                    MathJax.Hub.Queue([\"Typeset\",MathJax.Hub,\"editor-preview\"]);\r\n                    return preview.innerHTML;\r\n                },\r\n            });\r\n        })\r\n    </script>\r\n</head>\r\n\r\n<body>\r\n    <textarea id=\"md-editor\"></textarea>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>`\r\n\r\n**Avec  Katex**\r\n???', NULL, 1, NULL, 5, '<p><em>*Avec mathjax *</em><br />\nDÉMO : <a href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/1wkojtaa/3/\">https://jsfiddle.net/1wkojtaa/3/</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/chooco13/c280c1cc6584c97af85307028ecaebb1\">https://gist.github.com/chooco13/c280c1cc6584c97af85307028ecaebb1</a></p>\n\n<p>`[HTML_REMOVED]<br />\n[HTML_REMOVED]<br />\n    [HTML_REMOVED]<br />\n    [HTML_REMOVED][HTML_REMOVED]<br />\n    [HTML_REMOVED][HTML_REMOVED]<br />\n    [HTML_REMOVED][HTML_REMOVED]</p>\n\n<pre><code>[HTML_REMOVED]\n    $(function () {\n        MathJax.Hub.Config({\n            tex2jax: {inlineMath: [[\"$\",\"$\"],[\"\\\\(\",\"\\\\)\"]]}\n        });\n\n        var QUEUE = MathJax.Hub.queue;\n        var simplemde = new SimpleMDE({\n            element: document.getElementById(\"md-editor\"),\n            spellChecker: false,\n            previewRender: function(plainText) {\n                var preview = document.getElementsByClassName(\"editor-preview-side\")[0];\n                preview.innerHTML = this.parent.markdown(plainText);\n                preview.setAttribute(\'id\',\'editor-preview\')\n                MathJax.Hub.Queue([\"Typeset\",MathJax.Hub,\"editor-preview\"]);\n                return preview.innerHTML;\n            },\n        });\n    })\n[HTML_REMOVED]\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>[HTML_REMOVED]</p>\n\n<p>[HTML_REMOVED]<br />\n    [HTML_REMOVED][HTML_REMOVED]<br />\n[HTML_REMOVED]<br />\n[HTML_REMOVED]`</p>\n\n<p><strong>Avec  Katex</strong><br />\n???</p>', 1, 4, 1, NULL, 1),
